  Locus:
    Page: 429
    Verse: 7
Tags:
  - Silence
---
Do not even listen, simply wait. Do not even wait, be quiet, still and
solitary. The world will freely offer itself to you to be unmasked, it has
no choice, it will roll in ecstasy at your feet.
